12/* compares unterminated string 'str' with zero-terminated string 'cmp' */
13static inline int
14strncasecmpz(const char *str, const char *cmp, size_t len)
15{
16 if (strlen(cmp) != len)
17 return len;
18 return strncasecmp(str, cmp, len);
19}
